# Spotify Artist Explorer

This Android native application takes a keyword search and shows a list of artist names and their associated image. When the user taps an artist, it displays a separate screen which shows the artistâ€™s name,
their number of followers, and their associated image.

## Prerequisites

- Android Studio

### Installation

1. Clone the repository.
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/yourproject.git
2. Open project in Android studio
3. Make a raw file in the res folder and add spotify.properties with
  client_id="clientID"
  client_secret="clientSecret"
4. Setup Emulator on device manager based on specifications below.
5. Run emulator on app

#### Emulator Env

- Android Studio Emulator
- Pixel 7 API 25
- Android Nougat 7.1.1
